    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_2_7233-7249",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "7233-7249",
      "markText": "毅然戒去了昔日染上的吸大烟的恶习",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=7233&rangeEnd=7249",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=7233&rangeEnd=7249"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_11_17682-17749",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "17682-17749",
      "markText": "叶群是个心胸狭窄，嫉妒心极强的女人，得知事情原委后，她不分青红皂白，将一切不满迁怒到孙维世身上。无辜的孙维世，就这样日后竟遭杀身之祸。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=17682&rangeEnd=17749",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=17682&rangeEnd=17749"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_2_4071-4099",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "4071-4099",
      "markText": "志士恨无穷，只身走西东。　　投笔从戎去，刷新旧国风。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=4071&rangeEnd=4099",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=4071&rangeEnd=4099"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_2_2074-2157",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "2074-2157",
      "markText": "席先生是一位饱尝人世辛酸、思想开明的乡村知识分子。他痛恨恶势力，有追求报国救民真谛的精神，有强烈的民族自尊心和广博的学识。席先生的品行深深感化着、陶冶着成长中的朱德。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2074&rangeEnd=2157",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=2074&rangeEnd=2157"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_1_608-644",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "608-644",
      "markText": "林彪由于野心膨胀，阴谋篡党夺权，最后叛党叛国，彻底走向反面，为人所不齿。",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=608&rangeEnd=644",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=608&rangeEnd=644"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_6_10167-10212",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10167-10212",
      "markText": "陈毅说：“我国有句俗话，叫作‘聪明反被聪明误’。你这个人一生倒戈过7次，现在谁相信你嘛？”",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10167&rangeEnd=10212",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10167&rangeEnd=10212"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_2_3920-4006",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "3920-4006",
      "markText": "在仪陇县立高等小学堂一年的经历，朱德感受到了社会上旧势力的压迫和排挤，更看到了社会的腐败和黑暗，认识到“教书不是一条生路”，决心走一条新路。他要投笔从戎，寻找新的救国之路。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3920&rangeEnd=4006",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=3920&rangeEnd=4006"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_11_18573-18626",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "18573-18626",
      "markText": "在搞日救亡的潮流中，不知道她是通过什么途径，参加共产党领导的革命阵营，也不知道通过什么途径，又来到了延安。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=18573&rangeEnd=18626",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=18573&rangeEnd=18626"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_11_22062-22109",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "22062-22109",
      "markText": "可不是闹着玩的，刚刚打完天下，连气都没喘过来又要出国作战，而且是一个强手，万一有个三长两短的…",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=22062&rangeEnd=22109",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=22062&rangeEnd=22109"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "38131662_2_21873-21919",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "21873-21919",
      "markText": "“克清，我现在需要有一个像你这样纯洁、真诚、坚强的姑娘真心地爱我，我们结成终身伴侣，好吗？”",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=38131662&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=21873&rangeEnd=21919",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/531329f07245d7ce531595d?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=21873&rangeEnd=21919"
    },
    {
